               MOVE DBSQLI-MSG-TXT          TO   YCFCTLAR-LOG-CTNT(9:)
               ADD  DBSQLI-MSG-LEN  9   GIVING   YCFCTLAR-LOG-PTR
               PERFORM Z9990-USER-LOG-RTN  THRU Z9990-USER-LOG-EXT
             END-IF
      *
           END-PERFORM

